An alternative solution is that just remove tha parameter of request length in the implementation of encode_req, I think it is reasonable cause the spec don't have any request data except PLDM header.

Pseudo code:
```
LIBPLDM_ABI_TESTING
int encode_query_downstream_devices_req(uint8_t instance_id,
					struct pldm_msg *msg)
{
	if (msg == NULL) {
		return PLDM_ERROR_INVALID_DATA;
	}

	return encode_pldm_header_only(PLDM_REQUEST, instance_id, PLDM_FWUP,
				       PLDM_QUERY_DOWNSTREAM_DEVICES, msg);
}
